v></figure><p> 5月12日，该公司在其财务业绩材料中宣布了截至2024年3月31日的财年的几位新人才的首次亮相。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Hm8yzny65H"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/cover-corporation-plans-to-debut-new-talents-for-vtuber-agency-hololive-production-within-the-fiscal-year-ending-march-2024/">封面公司 VTuber 办公室 Hololive 制作新人亮相计划于截至 2024 年 3 月的财年</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“封面VTuber Office Hololive Production新人出道计划于2024年3月” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/cover-corporation-plans-to-debut-new-talents-for-vtuber-agency-hololive-production-within-the-fiscal-year-ending-march-2024/embed/#?secret=Lh8b8R633b#?secret=Hm8yzny65H" data-secret="Hm8yzny65H" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/hololivetv/status/1684035821052231685" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc_dgpKRj1k66eVpHBZt3Dzoo9sewK6kmtp1v_L7Hh1rxEI6YhWXWCyNa4Brn9ypiBCzntiVtzvMk8HT02tG7XuH8_yUuh_VAXzRd9-M6fpFz6GRYxAbc1VzDIEuZpVl-163QW5RpRrvPars-C_a8Xb1=w1097-h837-s-no" alt=""/></a> </figure><p></p><div class="pkqpl64c2eb8245838" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
