</style><h2 id="outline__2" class="wp-block-heading">Hololive英语-降临- </h2><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【#holoAdvent】通缉！【hololive 英文新单元首秀PV】" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dZrgAMWvIBA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><h3 id="outline__2_1" class="wp-block-heading">关于降临节</h3><p>降临人是从大监狱“The Cell”逃出来的同伙。由“西奥里·诺维拉”、“奈莉莎·拉文克罗夫特”、“古石宝石”、“不娃娃深渊守卫”、“莫科科深渊守卫”组成，进入大监狱的理由多种多样。只有一个目的。他们似乎在反抗世界、反抗命运、反抗无聊的日子。</p><h3 id="outline__2_2" class="wp-block-heading">关于《细胞》</h3><p>关押降临节成员的大型监狱。据说它位于世界某个地方的地下深处，但具体位置未知。它不限于人，它准备封印不可控的事物。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc-A5zc9es0-c9Q7DE4fzZ3VowbfkniIwVw2in7lb0PZgii7A_HzhgMlkBh_HnHLBixW3eY-eOWeTtfBYGETvqYLErzPhKu1ZHG3hPHHctXSgzqOIikfE0fEYt1Zc5sut8y7pNItiMiBSLy40hJMyNOi=w1097-h617-s-no" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://hololive.hololivepro.com/special/9028/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="来临">来临</a></p><cite>hololive官方网站</cite></blockquote><p></p><h2 id="outline__3" class="wp-block-heading">诗织中篇小说</h2><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="alignleft size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc89YNGtnp2PvvMN6gph8te8MUnm1_sGxwr_wpNwy5-GYHyCKDTpO0QNBi4lIKLYFmlvbibcMc9KgKGvD0RusmSByOz2zaAO-A7D6OO-t7TUHz6MXgDQ4qSltD7YjfmZquu2znfIQIl3EfVITf1ugACJ=w781-h1350-s-no" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure></div><p>一个受知识渴求驱使的“收藏家”。</p><p>我把我最喜欢的故事和珍贵的回忆变成书签并保存起来。</p><p>不幸的是，他被监禁了，因为他收集的故事中含有人类不应该接触的东西。然而，即使是这样的经历对她来说也可能是令人着迷的故事之一。为了了解未来的故事，我策划并执行了一次越狱。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>角色设计</td><td>かやはら (@kaya7hara)</td></tr><tr><td>公式チャンネル</td><td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ShioriNovella" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Shiori Novella Ch. hololive-EN">Shiori Novella Ch. hololive-EN</a></td></tr><tr><td> X (Twitter) 公式アカウント</td><td><a href="https://twitter.com/shiorinovella" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Shiori Novella &#x1f441;&#x200d;&#x1f5e8; holoEN">Shiori Novella <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f441.png" alt="👁" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ‍ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5e8.png" alt="🗨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> holoEN</a></td></tr><tr><td>デビュー配信予定日</td><td>2023年 (令和5年)<br> 7月30日 (日) 12時~ </td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="Prologue  #holoAdvent" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uEN-Mb5foz0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/shiorinovella/status/1684036360154349570" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc-CZMdIGYcZrWCHEKMHew90NsVvcjZ1Z2FN5Ug226RJr2l9JHxWpj2Pc2rrdVTyTwd7cTSRoKM9sqgikqgtrAV0OClFl0aI9XVJZPsrmsuaW4mi_gXE9RKZHnNPzxSFO5XjYHTUFl4Xnn0KDh98AGPq=w1097-h1320-s-no" alt=""/></a> </figure><p></p><div class="owkpe64c2eb82458de" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
